[b]TVO - The Agenda with Steve Paikin, October 12 2010: Anna Porter: The Ghosts of Europe | The Plight of the Roma[/b]

1) [u]The Interview: Anna Porter: Troubled Past, Uncertain Future[/u]

What is the state of democracy among former Eastern Bloc nations? Author, journalist and publisher Anna Porter joins [i]The Agenda[/i] to answer that question. 

[b]Anna Porter[/b] is author of [i]The Ghosts of Europe: Journeys Through Central Europe's Troubled Past and Uncertain Future[/i].

